title: Download your free official Australian bird of the year 2025 poster
summary: Guardian Australia and BirdLife Australia have released a free downloadable poster showcasing the artwork of Pete Cromer. The poster celebrates nature and wildlife, highlighting Cromer's unique artistic style. It is part of an initiative to promote awareness and appreciation for Australia’s biodiversity.

title: Tawny frogmouth named 2025 Australian bird of the year winner
summary: In the latest Guardian/BirdLife Australia poll, the perennial runner-up has finally emerged as the winner. The victory surpasses the Baudin’s black cockatoo and gang-gang cockatoo, which also received notable recognition. This biennial event celebrates Australia's favorite birds.
